{"tid":276802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【ISIS殺支那人】男女人質巴基斯坦遇害   支那外交部：正核實情況","createTime":"2017-06-09T05:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T06:45:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"394991f64ac57ef9570e467b39b9503fe4ab7eee","tid":276802,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1496968517_d190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1496968517_d190.jpg&h=97974f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）透過旗下通訊社表示，殺害兩名上月在巴基斯坦俾路支省綁架的一男一女支那公民。<br />\n<br />\n支那外交部表示，注意到有關報道，並對此表示嚴重關切。現時一直設法解救該兩名遭綁架人質。支方正通過各種途徑、包括巴基斯坦方面，了解核實有關情況。支方堅決反對一切形式的綁架平民行徑、反對一切形式的恐怖主義和極端暴力行徑。<br />\n<br />\n支那外交部"},{"pid":"aa15a5c0c3eb9f0429c20713e9feecf37756986e","tid":276802,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c5c2c7faf3856b5838ce52d67e2625e2f395ff","tid":276802,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"派架航空母艦去剷平ISIS啦"},{"pid":"d739d39ecb2ca14fa77e3365d0f7c3cd62ad7f18","tid":276802,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"殺晒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9a70e844a449d08c302928235e3fcc4aaa4f9f","tid":276802,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>派架航空母艦去剷平ISIS啦</blockquote><br />\n比人搶埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /中途係大海沉左"},{"pid":"2065325fe1e792c0b93531c33768928cf9151b7e","tid":276802,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"雜種幾時剷平ISIS<img src=\"/assets/face